A mythic and emotionally charged hero‚Äôs journey, ‚ÄúDune‚Äù tells the story of Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, who must travel to the most dangerous planet  in  the  universe  to  ensure  the  future  of  his  family  and  his  people.
